{
  "texts": [
    "Consequently, Fig. 7 was generated, depicting correlations between the Scopus keywords.",
    "These keywords were generated using an algorithm that detects repeated words and phrases forming the titles of the articles.",
    "While bibliometric analyses are rooted in data, their visual projection leans towards a qualitative analysis as the interpretation of the graph takes precedence over the raw data.",
    "As depicted in Fig. 7, five clusters were identified, with two markedly larger than the others.",
    "These two clusters are denoted in dark green (\"Virtual Reality\") and orange (\"three-dimensional computer graphics\").Interpreting these data reveals a meaningful disparity in the weight of keywords related to technology and VR compared to those associated with CH."
  ]
}